service_summaries.name: service_summaries
service_summaries.description: Service summary records linking claims to diagnoses

claims_services.name: claims_services
claims_services.description: Junction table linking claims to services

claims_to_diagnosis.sql: claims c JOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = CAST(c.diagnosis AS UNSIGNED) WHERE c.diagnosis REGEXP '^[0-9]+$'
claims_to_diagnosis.description: Link claims to diagnoses via claims.diagnosis TEXT column (contains diagnosis ID)

claims_to_services.sql: claims c JOIN claims_services cs ON cs.claims_id = c.id JOIN services s ON s.id = cs.services_id
claims_to_services.description: Link claims to medical services via junction table

claims_to_provider.sql: claims c JOIN providers p ON c.provider_id = p.id

claims_to_user.sql: claims c JOIN users u ON c.user_id = u.id

user_to_state.sql: users u JOIN states s ON u.state = s.id
user_to_state.description: Link users to their state for geographic filtering

claims_to_state.sql: claims c JOIN users u ON c.user_id = u.id JOIN states s ON u.state = s.id
claims_to_state.description: Link claims to states via user relationship
